HEADWORD: Richweed
<hw>Rich"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An herb (<spn>Pilea pumila</spn>) of the Nettle family, having a
smooth, juicy, pellucid stem; -- called also
<altname>clearweed</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ricinelaidic</ent>⟦br⟧
